---
/**
 * SiteFooter — copyright line + a Privacy Policy link.
 * Ben reduced this to copyright-only on 2026-06-17 (the wireframe's 6-link nav row
 * and email-capture form were dropped). The Privacy Policy link was added back
 * 2026-06-18 because LinkedIn Ads / a LinkedIn Company Page require a published,
 * linked privacy policy. Centered on the dark ground.
 *
 * Phone NOT shown here by design (Ben, 2026-06-26): a prominent number attracts the
 * wrong calls. The canonical line (615) 241-5635 lives ONLY as invisible
 * LocalBusiness JSON-LD `telephone` in BaseLayout (NAP / Google Business Profile /
 * SEO) — no visible click-to-call anywhere on the site.
 */
---

<footer class="site-footer section--dark" aria-label="Footer">
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="site-footer__links" aria-label="Footer">
      <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}privacy/`}>Privacy Policy</a>
    </nav>
    <p class="small site-footer__legal">© 2026 AV Ninjas. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    background: var(--color-ink);
    color: var(--color-canvas);
    padding-block: var(--space-3xl);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .site-footer__links {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  .site-footer__links a {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-canvas);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .site-footer__links a:hover { color: var(--color-accent-bright); }
  .site-footer__legal {
    color: var(--color-gray-bright);
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
